# Build Outputs (CONDITIONAL - MODIFIED BY DEPLOYMENT PIPELINE)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# NOTE: These patterns are REMOVED during WebGL deployment
# Template development: ignores build outputs
# Creator deployment: allows Build/ folder for GitHub Pages hosting

# Unity build directories (disabled during WebGL deployment)
/[Bb]uilds/
##WEBGL_DEPLOY_IGNORE_START##
/[Bb]uild/
Build/
